## 5. Database Column Map

| Payload field | DB table | DB column | Type | Notes |
|---------------|----------|-----------|------|-------|
| `poles[].pole_index` | `skycable_poles` | `pole_index` | `integer` | 1-based index assigned by AsBuilt |
| `poles[].pole_code` | `poles` | `pole_code` | `string` | Stored UPPERCASE |
| `poles[].latitude` | `poles` | `lat` | `decimal` | Required |
| `poles[].longitude` | `poles` | `lng` | `decimal` | Required |
| `spans[].strand_length` | `skycable_spans` + `skycable_span_summaries` | `strand_length` | `decimal` | Required |
| `spans[].number_of_runs` | `skycable_span_summaries` | `number_of_runs` | `integer` | Required |
| `spans[].components.*` | `skycable_span_summaries` | `expected_node`, `expected_amplifier`, etc. | `integer` | Defaults to 0 |
| `spans[].from_pole_index` | *(resolved in-memory, not stored)* | — | — | Used only to find the correct pole entry |
| `spans[].to_pole_index` | *(same)* | — | — | Same |
| — | `skycable_poles` | `sequence` | `integer` | **Reserved for PoleMaster (lineman teardown order). Never written from import payloads.** |

