## 8. Data Flow — DXF to AsBuilt IQ

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                         DXF DRAWING                              │
│  Contains: pole labels (text/strokes), cable lines, equipment   │
└────────────────────┬────────────────────────────────────────────┘
                     │
                     ▼
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                   1. POLE DETECTION (TrOCR)                      │
│  - Scans POLE layer for text entities and stroked labels        │
│  - Returns: [{ name, cx, cy, bbox, source }]                    │
│  - source: "text", "stroke", "geotool"                          │
└────────────────────┬────────────────────────────────────────────┘
                     │
                     ▼
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                   2. SPAN DETECTION (autoConnectPoles)           │
│  - Parses cable geometry lines                                  │
│  - Matches each span endpoint to the nearest pole               │
│  - Runs NPT dedup                                               │
│  - Returns: cableSpans[] with { from_pole, to_pole, meters }    │
└────────────────────┬────────────────────────────────────────────┘
                     │
                     ▼
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                   3. EXPORT (AsbuiltExportModal.tsx)             │
│  - Maps X-Y canvas coords → GPS (lat/lng) per pole              │
│  - Assigns pole_index = 1-based sequential (1, 2, 3 …)         │
│  - Builds poleIndexByPoleId lookup map                          │
│  - For each span: sets from_pole_index / to_pole_index          │
│  - Sets strand_length and number_of_runs (required)             │
│  - POSTs to /api/v1/asbuilt/import                              │
└────────────────────┬────────────────────────────────────────────┘
                     │
                     ▼
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                   4. LARAVEL BACKEND (AsBuiltController.php)     │
│  - Creates/updates Node by node_id + area_id                    │
│  - For each pole: match by pole_index → pole_code → create new  │
│  - Saves pole_index to skycable_poles.pole_index                │
│  - sequence column is never touched                             │
│  - For each span: resolves poles by from_pole_index/to_pole_index│
│  - No GPS fallback. No first-occurrence fallback.               │
│  - Missing index → span skipped, recorded in errors[]           │
│  - Returns: { node, poles_created, poles_updated,               │
│               spans_created, spans_updated, errors }            │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

